Continuous Integration (CI)

Developer push the code to a code repository often git, codecommit, bitbucket,..

A testing/build server checks the as soon as it's pushed ( codeBuild, Jenkins CI,...)

The developer gets feedback about the tests and checks that have passed/failed 

So with this we can find the big early and we fix them early 
Delivery faster as the code is tested 
Deploy often 


Continuous Delivery (CD)

